name: 娜塔莎·贾亚亨德里
name_full: 娜塔莎·贾亚亨德里 Natasha Jayahendry
introduction: Natasha Jayahendry is a British Indian actor represented by Janet Hampson Personal Management. She is known for playing Noor Inayat Khan in the 2022 U.K. theatre tour of World War II play, 'S.O.E' with Clair/Obscur Theatre Company. In September 2023, she is making her screen debut in the American television series, 'The Wheel of Time', Season 2, playing Cousin #1.
